{
  "stem": "26728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "So he spotted it, and he called the squadron in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we spent a day and a half.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We stopped it the front, which was just a strategy-- just-- and then, we just worked our way from both ends.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And it was just a, turkey shoot they called it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "There was nowhere for them to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And they couldn't get away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I mean, you could run into the woods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But we were shooting, and dropping bombs, and set the woods on fire for six, seven miles on both sides of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And it was a kind of a mountainous, curvy road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "It was really-- I never felt-- like sorry for these guys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "You know, I mean, they were enemy, and I hadn't seen the camps or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "But it was our job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And it wasn't-- it was an abstract thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "Which, if you talk to pilots, we'll tell you, it-- you're not looking at somebody in the eyes, you know, and killing them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "You're going 450, 500 miles an hour, pushing buttons, dropping the bombs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And all you see is a blur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you don't have to see the mess that you've made, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on this particular mission, it was such a turkey shoot, as we called it, that I-- I-- we talked about it later.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of us felt like, you know, that was too easy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was too easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no flak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no fighting back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, a little bit, but not-- it wasn't dangerous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It-- the biggest danger was hitting a tree or something, you know, which happened to a couple of guys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, that was-- that was really-- that was really an experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never forget that one.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
